1
00:00:06,356 --> 00:00:08,116
In the 15 days of new employee training,

2
00:00:08,116 --> 00:00:09,556
what's the first thing you learn?

3
00:00:09,556 --> 00:00:10,476
Do you know?

4
00:00:12,116 --> 00:00:12,915
Of course.

5
00:00:13,476 --> 00:00:15,476
Rule 1
of the new employee training manual:

6
00:00:16,355 --> 00:00:18,476
Strictly adhere
to the established hierarchy.

7
00:00:18,915 --> 00:00:20,275
Act according to your rank.

8
00:00:20,275 --> 00:00:21,236
Go to places you should.

9
00:00:21,236 --> 00:00:22,276
Do what you should.

10
00:00:22,596 --> 00:00:23,355
Exactly.

11
00:00:24,596 --> 00:00:25,515
Don't leave a shadow

12
00:00:25,515 --> 00:00:26,715
in places you shouldn't go.

13
00:00:27,035 --> 00:00:27,756
So,

14
00:00:27,756 --> 00:00:29,235
how are you going to explain

15
00:00:29,235 --> 00:00:30,355
you trespassing

16
00:00:30,355 --> 00:00:32,075
Room 666 at the Tian Level?

17
00:00:33,875 --> 00:00:34,996
If I say I was curious,

18
00:00:35,555 --> 00:00:36,436
do you believe that?

19
00:00:36,875 --> 00:00:38,075
But curiosity

20
00:00:38,435 --> 00:00:39,715
can get people killed.

21
00:00:41,035 --> 00:00:42,115
Like Yunyan

22
00:00:42,996 --> 00:00:44,236
or like

23
00:00:44,516 --> 00:00:45,556
An Ruoxi?

24
00:00:51,636 --> 00:00:52,556
Hand it over.

25
00:00:52,836 --> 00:00:54,276
You're An Ruoxi's sister, right?

26
00:00:56,715 --> 00:00:57,836
Does who I am matter?

27
00:00:58,516 --> 00:01:00,155
She gave you this bracelet, right?

28
00:01:00,475 --> 00:01:01,596
When did she give it to you?

29
00:01:06,516 --> 00:01:07,155
It's fine.

30
00:01:07,636 --> 00:01:08,715
If you don't want to say,

31
00:01:08,755 --> 00:01:09,715
I won't force you.

32
00:01:10,836 --> 00:01:11,836
But I'll say it again.

33
00:01:12,636 --> 00:01:13,756
Leave Deep In The Bustle.

34
00:01:13,916 --> 00:01:14,715
This isn't for you.

35
00:01:15,235 --> 00:01:16,036
I want to stay.

36
00:01:16,036 --> 00:01:17,435
I won't harm you, understand?

37
00:01:17,435 --> 00:01:18,355
I wish I could.

38
00:01:19,636 --> 00:01:20,595
But right now,

39
00:01:20,756 --> 00:01:22,196
I'm just confused.

40
00:01:24,996 --> 00:01:26,355
At Deep In The Bustle,

41
00:01:27,155 --> 00:01:28,476
sometimes being confused

42
00:01:29,116 --> 00:01:30,656
isn't a bad thing.

43
00:01:31,875 --> 00:01:32,556
Is that so?

44
00:01:33,676 --> 00:01:34,636
So confused

45
00:01:34,795 --> 00:01:36,875
that you'd believe any flimsy excuse

46
00:01:37,116 --> 00:01:38,636
the police come up with.

47
00:01:38,955 --> 00:01:39,680
Right?

48
00:01:42,528 --> 00:01:45,760
=The Glory Fades=

49
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:48,476
=Episode 13=
(Adventure)

50
00:01:48,476 --> 00:01:49,276
Ruxue.

51
00:01:49,515 --> 00:01:50,396
Come with me.

52
00:01:50,636 --> 00:01:52,036
A guest has requested your service.

53
00:01:52,396 --> 00:01:54,715
Although you're just a waitress now,

54
00:01:55,355 --> 00:01:57,196
being requested by a guest

55
00:01:57,476 --> 00:01:59,676
means your service fee
for the night doubles!

56
00:02:00,315 --> 00:02:00,916
The guest

57
00:02:00,916 --> 00:02:02,515
acknowledges your work ability.

58
00:02:03,155 --> 00:02:03,795
Let's go.

59
00:02:05,916 --> 00:02:08,036
I should've put on proper makeup.

60
00:02:08,096 --> 00:02:09,676
The service fee could double.

61
00:02:14,236 --> 00:02:14,956
Indeed,

62
00:02:15,475 --> 00:02:17,116
tonight's guest is quite special.

63
00:02:17,796 --> 00:02:18,276
So,

64
00:02:18,276 --> 00:02:20,035
let's go to the dressing room
to get ready.

65
00:02:20,595 --> 00:02:21,155
Really?

66
00:02:21,836 --> 00:02:22,475
Let's go.

67
00:02:29,035 --> 00:02:30,356
Meng Yin,

68
00:02:30,356 --> 00:02:31,755
I've brought you a girl.

69
00:02:31,796 --> 00:02:32,836
Could you do her makeup?

70
00:02:32,956 --> 00:02:34,315
A guest has requested her service.

71
00:02:34,956 --> 00:02:37,635
I need to finish Rose's makeup first.

72
00:02:37,635 --> 00:02:38,796
Mr. Lin is waiting.

73
00:02:38,796 --> 00:02:39,875
(Meng Yin, Head Makeup Artist)

74
00:02:39,875 --> 00:02:40,676
Will we make it?

75
00:02:42,996 --> 00:02:45,116
You're the best.

76
00:02:45,435 --> 00:02:46,315
Help me out.

77
00:02:46,836 --> 00:02:47,796
An assistant can

78
00:02:47,796 --> 00:02:49,116
just touch up my makeup.

79
00:02:51,315 --> 00:02:51,875
Come on,

80
00:02:52,155 --> 00:02:53,155
sit down.

81
00:02:53,996 --> 00:02:54,715
Su Yunian,

82
00:02:55,556 --> 00:02:56,556
say hello to Meng Yin,

83
00:02:56,556 --> 00:02:57,915
our head makeup artist.

84
00:02:58,035 --> 00:02:58,956
Hello, Meng Yin.

85
00:02:59,035 --> 00:02:59,996
Hello, Meng Yin.

86
00:03:01,836 --> 00:03:03,396
Such a clean face.

87
00:03:04,276 --> 00:03:04,915
You...

88
00:03:05,155 --> 00:03:06,035
Look at yourself.

89
00:03:06,035 --> 00:03:06,915
Where to apply makeup?

90
00:03:08,435 --> 00:03:09,875
You're joking.

91
00:03:10,035 --> 00:03:10,956
You flatter me.

92
00:03:11,396 --> 00:03:11,996
Meng Yin,

93
00:03:12,076 --> 00:03:13,875
you have seen all kinds of beauties.

94
00:03:14,035 --> 00:03:16,396
You know Mr. Tu has his eye on her,

95
00:03:16,556 --> 00:03:18,635
so you're just finding ways
to flatter her.

96
00:03:18,715 --> 00:03:19,996
Mr. Tu has his eye on her?

97
00:03:20,116 --> 00:03:21,556
Do I know that?

98
00:03:22,144 --> 00:03:22,656
Enough.

99
00:03:22,656 --> 00:03:23,915
Are you done yet?

100
00:03:24,116 --> 00:03:24,996
Hurry up!

101
00:03:25,356 --> 00:03:26,475
You have half an hour.

102
00:03:26,475 --> 00:03:27,595
An Ruoxi must be ready.

103
00:03:27,915 --> 00:03:28,356
That's it.

104
00:03:28,356 --> 00:03:29,595
Come pick her up in 15 minutes.

105
00:03:29,875 --> 00:03:30,315
Got it.

106
00:03:30,435 --> 00:03:31,435
I'll get back to work.

107
00:03:33,035 --> 00:03:34,595
I still have two VIP rooms to assign.

108
00:03:35,155 --> 00:03:36,915
Ever since Yunyan left,

109
00:03:36,915 --> 00:03:38,755
all these tasks pile up on me.

110
00:03:38,755 --> 00:03:39,635
So annoying.

111
00:03:41,556 --> 00:03:43,155
Alright, I'll pick you up later.

112
00:03:47,116 --> 00:03:47,836
I heard

113
00:03:47,836 --> 00:03:49,556
Ruxue is dominating everything now.

114
00:03:49,755 --> 00:03:50,796
As you're following her,

115
00:03:50,796 --> 00:03:52,356
could she promote you?

116
00:03:52,635 --> 00:03:55,155
All resources are compiled
and distributed by Ms. Bai.

117
00:03:55,276 --> 00:03:56,396
Whether I get promoted

118
00:03:56,715 --> 00:03:58,715
depends on my performance.

119
00:04:00,116 --> 00:04:00,715
Miss,

120
00:04:01,356 --> 00:04:03,236
your surname is Su, right?

121
00:04:03,475 --> 00:04:04,076
Yes.

122
00:04:04,276 --> 00:04:04,956
Your full name?

123
00:04:05,315 --> 00:04:06,396
Su Yunian.

124
00:04:06,635 --> 00:04:08,076
Such a poetic name.

125
00:04:09,035 --> 00:04:11,116
You must come from a scholarly family.

126
00:04:11,435 --> 00:04:13,595
My mother adored Tang and Song poetry.

127
00:04:13,996 --> 00:04:15,715
When she named me,

128
00:04:15,715 --> 00:04:17,035
she was reading the line:

129
00:04:17,315 --> 00:04:19,076
Cherish fragrance,
pluck blooms on the islet.

130
00:04:19,475 --> 00:04:20,956
That's how she chose my name.

131
00:04:23,195 --> 00:04:25,515
My mother was passionate
about Tang and Song poetry.

132
00:04:25,796 --> 00:04:27,476
Back when naming me,

133
00:04:27,476 --> 00:04:29,875
she was reading Bai Juyi's 'Night Rain'.

134
00:04:30,676 --> 00:04:32,315
I think of my beloved,

135
00:04:32,635 --> 00:04:34,036
so far away in that distant land.

136
00:04:34,156 --> 00:04:35,515
Hence, my name came to be.

137
00:04:36,275 --> 00:04:37,476
Truly a family of arts.

138
00:04:37,476 --> 00:04:38,835
I've never heard those two lines.

139
00:04:39,835 --> 00:04:41,676
Your siblings must have
beautiful names too.

140
00:04:42,515 --> 00:04:43,356
Pretty much.

141
00:04:43,515 --> 00:04:44,916
All derived from poetry.

142
00:04:45,515 --> 00:04:46,835
My mother often said,

143
00:04:46,835 --> 00:04:48,356
"Good thing we didn't have boys.

144
00:04:48,556 --> 00:04:50,676
Otherwise, these artistic names
wouldn't be used."

145
00:04:51,875 --> 00:04:53,356
So your siblings

146
00:04:53,356 --> 00:04:54,635
have lovely names too?

147
00:04:56,996 --> 00:04:57,716
Meng Yin,

148
00:04:58,075 --> 00:04:59,515
should I make the eyebrows darker?

149
00:04:59,515 --> 00:05:00,515
It's a bit light.

150
00:05:03,755 --> 00:05:05,275
Want them more defined?

151
00:05:05,476 --> 00:05:06,556
Let me add some color.

152
00:05:19,556 --> 00:05:20,116
Go ahead.

153
00:05:20,796 --> 00:05:22,716
Fifteen. Twenty.

154
00:05:24,156 --> 00:05:25,755
Fifteen. Twenty. Fifteen.

155
00:05:26,635 --> 00:05:28,116
You definitely drank!

156
00:05:28,676 --> 00:05:30,356
You're cheating again!

157
00:05:30,356 --> 00:05:31,515
Fifteen.

158
00:05:35,796 --> 00:05:37,275
Good evening, honored guests.

159
00:05:37,356 --> 00:05:38,755
My name is Su Yunian.

160
00:05:38,875 --> 00:05:40,596
I'm delighted to have the opportunity

161
00:05:40,596 --> 00:05:41,996
to serve you all tonight.

162
00:05:45,036 --> 00:05:45,596
Alright.

163
00:05:45,996 --> 00:05:47,635
Fifteen. Twenty.

164
00:05:47,635 --> 00:05:48,315
Fifteen.

165
00:05:49,476 --> 00:05:51,315
You, you drank!

166
00:05:51,315 --> 00:05:51,916
Cheating again.

167
00:05:51,916 --> 00:05:53,116
Fifteen. Twenty.

168
00:05:53,116 --> 00:05:53,875
Fifteen.

169
00:05:54,716 --> 00:05:55,435
Fifteen. Twenty.

170
00:05:55,435 --> 00:05:56,236
Fifteen.

171
00:05:57,088 --> 00:05:59,275
Your cheating's getting worse.

172
00:05:59,275 --> 00:06:00,156
How can you do this?

173
00:06:00,476 --> 00:06:01,716
Fifteen. Twenty.

174
00:06:01,716 --> 00:06:02,315
Fifteen.

175
00:06:02,395 --> 00:06:03,236
Enough!

176
00:06:12,835 --> 00:06:13,835
Good evening, Mr. Lin.

177
00:06:14,116 --> 00:06:14,596
Good.

178
00:06:14,755 --> 00:06:15,435
Very good.

179
00:06:16,075 --> 00:06:17,275
You're

180
00:06:17,275 --> 00:06:18,556
Su Yunian, right?

181
00:06:19,075 --> 00:06:19,835
Seems

182
00:06:21,996 --> 00:06:23,796
we're quite fated.

183
00:06:23,796 --> 00:06:24,356
Look,

184
00:06:24,356 --> 00:06:25,275
we meet again.

185
00:06:27,236 --> 00:06:28,515
Mr. Lin, you flatter me.

186
00:06:28,875 --> 00:06:31,515
Since you requested me tonight,

187
00:06:31,716 --> 00:06:32,716
I'll strive

188
00:06:32,716 --> 00:06:33,755
to give my absolute best.

189
00:06:35,676 --> 00:06:36,556
You're

190
00:06:36,955 --> 00:06:37,755
quite sensible.

191
00:06:38,356 --> 00:06:39,036
Alright.

192
00:06:39,515 --> 00:06:41,676
If you can please me tonight,

193
00:06:41,676 --> 00:06:43,356
every hostess here,

194
00:06:43,515 --> 00:06:45,116
and the servers pouring drinks,

195
00:06:45,515 --> 00:06:47,195
will get double tips.

196
00:06:48,556 --> 00:06:49,315
However,

197
00:06:49,996 --> 00:06:51,236
that being said,

198
00:06:51,676 --> 00:06:53,315
if I'm not satisfied,

199
00:06:53,676 --> 00:06:54,395
what then?

200
00:06:57,635 --> 00:06:58,596
I'll do my best.

201
00:07:06,955 --> 00:07:07,916
Don't just sit there!

202
00:07:08,435 --> 00:07:09,515
Get wild!

203
00:07:09,996 --> 00:07:10,875
Come on.

204
00:07:10,875 --> 00:07:11,916
Let's play dice.

205
00:07:15,356 --> 00:07:16,416
- Hello, Ms. Bai.
- Hello, Ms. Bai.

206
00:07:19,755 --> 00:07:20,556
Ms. Bai.

207
00:07:21,916 --> 00:07:23,515
Ms. Bai, are you heading upstairs?

208
00:07:23,955 --> 00:07:24,635
Yes.

209
00:07:26,176 --> 00:07:26,875
By the way,

210
00:07:27,156 --> 00:07:28,395
about Su Yunian,

211
00:07:28,635 --> 00:07:29,476
is it arranged?

212
00:07:30,116 --> 00:07:31,156
Don't worry.

213
00:07:31,275 --> 00:07:32,256
It's all taken care of.

214
00:07:32,256 --> 00:07:33,515
I guarantee that after tonight,

215
00:07:33,515 --> 00:07:34,635
she won't come to work.

216
00:07:35,796 --> 00:07:37,156
Just make sure she isn't hurt.

217
00:07:37,476 --> 00:07:38,676
Make her get the hint

218
00:07:38,676 --> 00:07:39,755
and resign voluntarily.

219
00:07:40,896 --> 00:07:41,796
Ms. Bai,

220
00:07:42,996 --> 00:07:44,835
what's going on with her?

221
00:07:44,835 --> 00:07:46,156
Over these years,

222
00:07:46,156 --> 00:07:47,676
I've never seen you dismiss anyone.

223
00:07:48,036 --> 00:07:49,635
- Because she looks like...
- Ms. Bai!

224
00:07:52,275 --> 00:07:53,075
Anything else?

225
00:07:54,596 --> 00:07:55,435
Ms. Bai,

226
00:07:55,676 --> 00:07:57,275
this is the beauty broth I made for you.

227
00:07:57,435 --> 00:07:58,916
You've looked quite worn out lately.

228
00:07:59,075 --> 00:08:00,075
Drink to nourish you.

229
00:08:03,596 --> 00:08:04,515
Thank you, Ruxue.

230
00:08:06,075 --> 00:08:07,156
We're fellow townsfolk

231
00:08:07,356 --> 00:08:08,236
with the same surname.

232
00:08:09,515 --> 00:08:10,395
All these years,

233
00:08:10,395 --> 00:08:12,036
I've thought of you as my own sister.

234
00:08:13,435 --> 00:08:14,875
I want to tell you something.

235
00:08:15,556 --> 00:08:16,356
Please go ahead.

236
00:08:17,596 --> 00:08:18,755
Stay away from trouble.

237
00:08:19,356 --> 00:08:20,676
Focus on your own duties.

238
00:08:21,916 --> 00:08:23,315
Don't end up like Yunyan.

239
00:08:25,356 --> 00:08:26,236
I see.

240
00:08:26,236 --> 00:08:27,075
Thank you.

241
00:08:31,356 --> 00:08:32,596
Mr. Lin,

242
00:08:32,596 --> 00:08:34,156
you're too good.

243
00:08:34,236 --> 00:08:36,195
I lose every time I play against you.

244
00:08:36,875 --> 00:08:38,476
I choose

245
00:08:38,915 --> 00:08:40,956
Dare.

246
00:08:41,476 --> 00:08:42,155
Okay.

247
00:08:42,956 --> 00:08:45,236
Then I'll give you an easy one.

248
00:08:46,555 --> 00:08:47,755
Make Su Yunian

249
00:08:48,155 --> 00:08:49,155
drink this.

250
00:08:50,675 --> 00:08:51,755
Easy.

251
00:08:52,515 --> 00:08:53,076
You,

252
00:08:53,275 --> 00:08:53,755
come here.

253
00:08:54,236 --> 00:08:55,035
Come on!

254
00:09:00,035 --> 00:09:00,836
Drink this.

255
00:09:02,515 --> 00:09:03,236
I'm sorry.

256
00:09:03,236 --> 00:09:04,196
I have work to do.

257
00:09:04,196 --> 00:09:05,035
I can't drink.

258
00:09:12,915 --> 00:09:14,515
You drink when I tell you to.

259
00:09:14,515 --> 00:09:16,155
Don't make Mr. Lin unhappy.

260
00:09:22,635 --> 00:09:23,635
Aya,

261
00:09:24,436 --> 00:09:25,716
I was thinking

262
00:09:25,956 --> 00:09:27,996
if you could complete this dare,

263
00:09:28,436 --> 00:09:30,275
I'd give you this stack of cash.

264
00:09:30,596 --> 00:09:31,596
Too bad,

265
00:09:31,996 --> 00:09:32,755
you can't take it.

266
00:09:37,275 --> 00:09:38,476
Su Yunian,

267
00:09:39,836 --> 00:09:41,875
you know I'm here to make money.

268
00:09:42,236 --> 00:09:43,675
This stack of cash

269
00:09:43,675 --> 00:09:45,956
is enough to support my family
for a month.

270
00:09:46,476 --> 00:09:48,675
Your pride is your own business.

271
00:09:48,875 --> 00:09:49,915
But

272
00:09:50,035 --> 00:09:51,675
at this place,

273
00:09:51,675 --> 00:09:53,275
a guest asking you to drink

274
00:09:53,316 --> 00:09:55,395
isn't exactly outrageous.

275
00:09:55,875 --> 00:09:57,076
Then half this money

276
00:09:57,076 --> 00:09:58,996
should go to Su Yunian.

277
00:10:04,356 --> 00:10:05,996
If you still refuse to drink,

278
00:10:06,555 --> 00:10:08,755
I'll have to complain
to the supervisor about you

279
00:10:08,836 --> 00:10:10,155
and you can expect to be fired.

280
00:10:10,395 --> 00:10:11,915
(You do bear some resemblance.)

281
00:10:12,196 --> 00:10:14,035
I almost thought you were sisters.

282
00:10:18,236 --> 00:10:20,836
Since we look somewhat alike,

283
00:10:21,076 --> 00:10:22,875
I wonder if it could be my blessing

284
00:10:23,155 --> 00:10:25,316
and my chance to climb higher.

285
00:10:28,675 --> 00:10:29,476
Alright.

286
00:10:30,436 --> 00:10:32,275
I won't force you to leave.

287
00:10:33,236 --> 00:10:34,555
I'll give you three days.

288
00:10:34,956 --> 00:10:36,076
If within three days,

289
00:10:36,675 --> 00:10:38,035
you can handle these guests

290
00:10:38,035 --> 00:10:39,356
without receiving any complaints,

291
00:10:41,316 --> 00:10:42,316
then I'll agree

292
00:10:42,675 --> 00:10:43,996
to let you move up a level.

293
00:10:44,476 --> 00:10:45,196
Fine.

294
00:10:45,436 --> 00:10:46,836
But what if you fail?

295
00:10:48,996 --> 00:10:50,035
Then I'll resign

296
00:10:50,716 --> 00:10:51,915
and leave Deep In The Bustle.

297
00:10:53,555 --> 00:10:54,356
Deal.

298
00:10:55,116 --> 00:10:55,956
Deal.

299
00:11:02,596 --> 00:11:03,515
Thanks.

300
00:11:08,275 --> 00:11:09,515
How was that, Mr. Lin?

301
00:11:09,875 --> 00:11:11,035
Well done.

302
00:11:11,755 --> 00:11:12,555
It's your reward.

303
00:11:13,476 --> 00:11:14,795
You're the best.

304
00:11:15,155 --> 00:11:16,236
My turn.

305
00:11:24,795 --> 00:11:26,155
I lost again.

306
00:11:29,836 --> 00:11:31,155
I want to play Dare too.

307
00:11:32,515 --> 00:11:33,716
Mr. Lin,

308
00:11:34,356 --> 00:11:36,035
the same task?

309
00:11:36,716 --> 00:11:37,555
Of course.

310
00:11:37,836 --> 00:11:39,076
For fairness,

311
00:11:39,116 --> 00:11:40,116
all gets the same task.

312
00:11:41,116 --> 00:11:41,716
Fine.

313
00:11:47,596 --> 00:11:48,196
Drink it.

314
00:11:52,076 --> 00:11:52,755
Sorry.

315
00:11:53,116 --> 00:11:53,996
Only that glass.

316
00:11:54,316 --> 00:11:55,275
After that one,

317
00:11:55,275 --> 00:11:56,795
I won't drink any more alcohol.

318
00:12:01,356 --> 00:12:02,635
I said drink it!

319
00:12:02,836 --> 00:12:04,635
Why drink hers but not mine?

320
00:12:05,356 --> 00:12:05,915
Listen.

321
00:12:05,915 --> 00:12:07,196
You must drink it today!

322
00:12:07,196 --> 00:12:07,996
I can't.

323
00:12:12,116 --> 00:12:13,635
I'm telling you to drink it!

324
00:12:13,956 --> 00:12:15,155
You're crazy!

325
00:12:19,356 --> 00:12:20,236
Mr. Lin,

326
00:12:20,635 --> 00:12:21,716
that task

327
00:12:21,956 --> 00:12:23,196
is finished, right?

328
00:12:25,196 --> 00:12:26,196
Yes.

329
00:12:26,476 --> 00:12:27,275
But,

330
00:12:28,035 --> 00:12:29,116
she didn't drink enough.

331
00:12:29,795 --> 00:12:30,596
Deduct two notes.

332
00:12:34,196 --> 00:12:35,155
Mr. Lin,

333
00:12:35,596 --> 00:12:36,996
you're so kind.

334
00:12:37,836 --> 00:12:38,596
Enough.

335
00:12:38,596 --> 00:12:39,356
Everyone!

336
00:12:40,035 --> 00:12:40,996
Stop rolling the dice.

337
00:12:41,755 --> 00:12:42,635
All of you,

338
00:12:42,635 --> 00:12:43,875
do this together

339
00:12:44,356 --> 00:12:45,915
and make Su Yunian drink.

340
00:12:46,515 --> 00:12:47,675
For every glass she drinks,

341
00:12:47,915 --> 00:12:49,275
you get a stack of cash.

342
00:12:49,635 --> 00:12:51,155
The more she drinks,

343
00:12:51,635 --> 00:12:52,875
the more you earn.

344
00:12:54,555 --> 00:12:55,436
Mr. Lin,

345
00:12:55,436 --> 00:12:57,236
what's fun about this?

346
00:12:57,236 --> 00:12:58,196
Let's play another game

347
00:12:58,196 --> 00:12:59,196
you've never played.

348
00:12:59,555 --> 00:13:00,196
Get lost.

349
00:13:01,476 --> 00:13:02,275
What are you doing?

350
00:13:02,395 --> 00:13:03,196
Go on! Now!

351
00:13:04,996 --> 00:13:05,795
Okay.

352
00:13:15,436 --> 00:13:16,236
Drink, come on!

353
00:13:16,635 --> 00:13:17,436
Drink!

354
00:13:18,675 --> 00:13:19,716
You go over too.

355
00:13:20,395 --> 00:13:21,196
Drink!

356
00:13:22,076 --> 00:13:22,875
Drink.

357
00:13:23,555 --> 00:13:24,356
Drink.

358
00:13:24,395 --> 00:13:25,196
Drink!

359
00:13:26,275 --> 00:13:27,076
Drink, come on!

360
00:13:30,956 --> 00:13:31,755
Why refuse?

361
00:13:32,035 --> 00:13:33,236
Just a little alcohol.

362
00:13:50,116 --> 00:13:51,996
Su Yunian is kind of pitiful.

363
00:13:52,316 --> 00:13:53,696
Has a legit double degree,

364
00:13:53,696 --> 00:13:55,116
but ends up doing this.

365
00:13:57,436 --> 00:13:58,515
Don't you think she looks

366
00:13:59,116 --> 00:14:00,275
a bit like Ruoxi?

367
00:14:02,795 --> 00:14:04,076
You talk too much.

368
00:14:04,755 --> 00:14:06,316
Arrange a car for her later.

369
00:14:06,716 --> 00:14:08,116
Don't let anything happen.

370
00:14:11,395 --> 00:14:12,116
Alright.

371
00:14:12,515 --> 00:14:13,915
You know how to cherish beauty.

372
00:14:20,236 --> 00:14:21,836
Since she looks so much like her,

373
00:14:21,956 --> 00:14:23,436
don't you plan on keeping her

374
00:14:23,836 --> 00:14:25,035
to project your feelings?

375
00:14:28,555 --> 00:14:29,356
Forget it.

376
00:14:30,596 --> 00:14:31,395
Back to business.

377
00:14:32,076 --> 00:14:34,795
Last time we stood up Mr. Tang.

378
00:14:34,956 --> 00:14:36,436
He was pretty pissed off.

379
00:14:37,116 --> 00:14:38,956
Shouldn't we make it up to him?

380
00:14:48,275 --> 00:14:49,076
How about this?

381
00:14:49,635 --> 00:14:51,436
The Beauty Contest is in three days.

382
00:14:52,236 --> 00:14:53,236
Invite him over

383
00:14:53,436 --> 00:14:54,236
and drink with him.

384
00:14:54,836 --> 00:14:55,956
We'll go to his place later.

385
00:14:57,155 --> 00:14:57,956
Sincere enough, huh?

386
00:14:58,675 --> 00:14:59,515
Fine.

387
00:14:59,515 --> 00:15:00,476
Max out the prestige!

388
00:15:00,476 --> 00:15:01,316
I'll arrange it.

389
00:15:03,996 --> 00:15:06,275
If you're not interested in her,

390
00:15:06,596 --> 00:15:07,956
I might make a move.

391
00:15:13,356 --> 00:15:13,996
Fine.

392
00:15:13,996 --> 00:15:14,996
You just stay single.

393
00:15:15,515 --> 00:15:16,635
Stay single.

394
00:15:32,356 --> 00:15:33,035
Yunian,

395
00:15:34,035 --> 00:15:35,035
what happened to you?

396
00:15:35,035 --> 00:15:36,555
I was only gone for a short while.

397
00:15:36,836 --> 00:15:38,395
Did they already go after you?

398
00:15:40,635 --> 00:15:42,155
If I'd known, I wouldn't have left.

399
00:15:42,436 --> 00:15:43,040
If I were here,

400
00:15:43,040 --> 00:15:44,836
those wretches wouldn't have dared.

401
00:15:44,836 --> 00:15:46,155
Come on, drink some water.

402
00:15:46,555 --> 00:15:46,996
Here.

403
00:15:56,316 --> 00:15:57,635
It's all my fault, Yunian.

404
00:15:57,635 --> 00:15:58,236
My fault.

405
00:15:58,596 --> 00:16:00,275
It's all right.

406
00:16:02,196 --> 00:16:03,035
In my opinion,

407
00:16:03,035 --> 00:16:03,956
as a college student,

408
00:16:03,956 --> 00:16:05,395
you really don't belong here.

409
00:16:05,675 --> 00:16:06,316
How about this?

410
00:16:06,675 --> 00:16:07,915
I'll talk to Ms. Bai

411
00:16:07,915 --> 00:16:09,116
to get you extra bonus.

412
00:16:09,116 --> 00:16:10,076
Quit tomorrow.

413
00:16:10,076 --> 00:16:10,836
Okay?

414
00:16:15,155 --> 00:16:15,596
Come on.

415
00:16:15,716 --> 00:16:16,755
Drink some more water.

416
00:16:16,795 --> 00:16:17,836
This won't do.

417
00:16:17,836 --> 00:16:19,275
There's honey and lemon in it.

418
00:16:19,635 --> 00:16:20,555
Quick, be good.

419
00:16:21,116 --> 00:16:21,555
Drink it.

420
00:16:21,555 --> 00:16:22,716
Or it'll upset your stomach.

421
00:16:33,875 --> 00:16:35,316
Thank you, Ruxue.

422
00:16:35,316 --> 00:16:36,515
Warm is better.

423
00:16:38,515 --> 00:16:39,476
Actually,

424
00:16:39,795 --> 00:16:41,395
I have a sister at home,

425
00:16:41,476 --> 00:16:43,476
who's about your age.

426
00:16:44,116 --> 00:16:45,596
If you don't mind,

427
00:16:45,675 --> 00:16:47,236
think of me as your own sister.

428
00:16:47,555 --> 00:16:49,275
I'll look out for you here.

429
00:16:51,515 --> 00:16:52,096
Come on.

430
00:16:52,096 --> 00:16:52,996
One last sip.

431
00:16:52,996 --> 00:16:53,555
Be good.

432
00:16:53,555 --> 00:16:54,076
Drink it.

433
00:16:54,316 --> 00:16:55,076
Finish it,

434
00:16:55,076 --> 00:16:56,316
then change your clothes.

435
00:16:56,356 --> 00:16:57,476
I'll take you home.

436
00:16:57,476 --> 00:16:57,875
Alright?

437
00:16:58,076 --> 00:16:59,116
Come on. Get up.

438
00:17:08,755 --> 00:17:09,395
Okay.

439
00:17:09,956 --> 00:17:10,555
Let's go.

440
00:17:10,555 --> 00:17:11,275
Come on.

441
00:17:18,515 --> 00:17:19,275
Take it slow.

442
00:17:33,140 --> 00:17:36,814
♪If the heart can't hear the sorrow♪

443
00:17:37,113 --> 00:17:40,304
♪It only makes everything look so fake♪

444
00:17:41,984 --> 00:17:45,757
♪Your eyes resemble hers too much♪

445
00:17:46,306 --> 00:17:49,105
♪Who makes me forget whom♪

446
00:17:50,576 --> 00:17:54,306
♪The warmth in my heart is fading♪

447
00:17:54,530 --> 00:17:58,144
♪Every glance feels like atonement♪

448
00:17:59,426 --> 00:18:03,113
♪Ambiguity hidden in the night breeze♪

449
00:18:03,751 --> 00:18:08,866
♪Blows away the chance to explain♪

450
00:18:09,570 --> 00:18:13,704
♪I feel guilty♪

451
00:18:14,274 --> 00:18:18,018
♪I'll have no regrets
even I leave quietly♪

452
00:18:18,882 --> 00:18:22,325
♪Even in tears♪

453
00:18:23,074 --> 00:18:26,988
♪It doesn't matter♪

454
00:18:27,170 --> 00:18:30,993
♪We embrace in dreams♪

455
00:18:31,842 --> 00:18:35,280
♪I let down all my defenses♪

456
00:18:36,514 --> 00:18:39,877
♪Though the story has its end♪

457
00:18:40,642 --> 00:18:48,994
♪I'll journey with you all my life♪
